http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/columnists/otb/NC/mcdo0725.html 204.71.237.74 19970108092143 text/html 4916
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 09:21:56 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 19-Aug-96 16:42:07 GMT
Content-length: 4730
