<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/columnists/otb/WA/malkin4.html 204.71.237.74 19970108092427 text/html 6533
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 09:24:43 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 03-Sep-96 18:11:24 GMT
Content-length: 6346
