<a name="Florida"></a>FLORIDA		-Florida Tax Cap Committee
			-Revenue  limitation,  tax limitation
			(voter approval of new taxes/fees)
		-Just one tax
		-Voter approval of city taxes
<hr>
<a name="Idaho"></a>IDAHO		-School tax credits
<hr>
<a name="Massachusetts"></a>MASSACHUSETTS	-Free the Pike-User fee's removed on toll road
		-Repeal excise tax on registered motor vehicles
		-Sales tax reform
		-Repeal sales tax on telecommunications and 
			consumer electronics
