<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/whois/hamrick.html">Kristi Stone Hamrick</A>,<I> Press Secretary</I>
<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/whois/hansen.html">Kristin Hansen</A>,<I> Assistant
 Press Secretary</I>
<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/whois/hsu.html">Gracie S. Hsu</A>,<I> Health and Reproductive Analyst</I>
