<center><H2><font color="yellow">ISSUES</font><br> 
<font color="red">'96</font></h2>
<b><font color="red">The Candidate's Briefing Book</font><p>

<i>Edited by Stuart M. Butler <br>
and<br>
 Kim R. Holmes</i>
<p><a href="/heritage">The Heritage Foundation</a><br></b>
214 Massachusetts Ave, N.E.<br>
Washington, D.C. 20002

<p>

<P><B><a href="about.html">About Issues 1996</a>                 
<p><a href="#P1">Part I: Domestic and Economic Policy Issues</a><br>
<p><a href="#P2">Part II: Foreign Policy and National Security Issues</a>
</B>
</center>
<p>
