<P><B><a href="chpt8.html">CRIME</a>&#160; &#160; <a href="/heritage/issues96/pdf/chap_8.pdf"><b>.pdf version</b></a>
</B></P>
<P>&#160;&#160;<B><i>By <a href="/heritage/staff/fagan.htm">Patrick F. Fagan</a> and <a href="/heritage/staff/moffit.htm">Robert E. Moffit</a></i>          
</P>
<P>
<font size="-1">
<P><A HREF="chpt8.html#ISSUES">The Issues</A>  | 
<A HREF="chpt8.html#FACTS">The Facts</A>  | 
