<li><a href="inapr6p.html">April 1996 Issue -- Publication Reviews</a>
<p>
<li><a href="inmarfea.html">March 1996 issue -- Understanding Corporate Government Relations</a> by <a href="/heritage/staff/gaynerl.htm">Lewis F. Gayner</a>
<li><a href="inmarpub.html">March 1996 issue -- Publication Reviews</a>
<p>
<li><a href="infebfeat.html">February 1996 issue -- The Environmental Establishment: A Status Report</a> by Jonathan Adler
<li><a href="infebbkrv.html">February 1996 issue -- In Focus: Book Review</a>
<li><a href="infebpubs.html">February 1996 issue -- Publication Reviews</a> 
<p>
<li><a href="indecftr.html">December-January 1996 issue -- Policy Review: The Journal of American Citizenship</a> by <a href="/heritage/staff/meyerson.htm">Adam Meyerson</a>
<li><a href="indecrvw.html">December-January 1996 issue -- In Focus: Book Review</a>
<li><a href="indecpub.html">December-January 1996 issue -- Publication Reviews</a>
