<head>
<title>The Salviatori Leadership Speakers Bureau</title>
</head>

<body>
<center>
<img alt="The Salvitori Leadership Speakers Bureau" src="sb-logo.gif">
</center>
<p>
The mission of the Salvatori Leadership Speakers Bureau is to promote on campus America's first principles and to defend the values of the Founding Fathers: the ideas of free enterprise, limited government, strong national defense and traditional family values.<p>

Although these speakers would not agree on all issues, each of them represents aspects of the winning conservative coalition in the United States, values and ideas which are over looked on most campuses.<p>
<p>
Currently, we are in the process of updating
our Salvatori Leadership Speakers Bureau web page. All of the speaker descriptions are being updated and new speakers are being added. The new web page will be
posted as soon as the updates are finished. If you would like information on
this Leadership Institute program please <a href="mailto:lead@lead-inst.org"><img src="email2.gif" ALT="email" BORDER=0 ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE></a> or call Ken Weary at
1-800-827-LEAD.

<p>
Available Speakers include:
<b><p>
The Honorable Gary Bauer<br>
