<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/abic/gopwoman.html.cgi 204.71.237.74 19970108094400 text/html 7646
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 09:44:15 GMT
