<img src="/crc/images/pcp10w.gif" alt="Ten Worst Corporate Misgivers" border="0"><br>
<ul>
<pre>
<B>Company		 	Rating		Grade</b>

<a href="pcp10w.html#coca_cola">Coca-Cola</a>		2.27		F
